  "response": "Tata Motors is an Indian automotive manufacturing company that produces a variety of passenger and commercial vehicles. As of 2023, here are some of the cars offered by Tata Motors in their passenger vehicle segment:\n\n### Hatchbacks:\n1. **Tata Tiago**\n2. **Tata Altroz**\n3. **Tata Bolt** (Though production may have ceased, earlier models could still be available in the market)\n\n### Sedans:\n1. **Tata Tigor**\n\n### SUVs/Crossovers:\n1. **Tata Nexon**\n2. **Tata Harrier**\n3. **Tata Safari**\n4. **Tata Punch**\n5. **Tata Nexon EV** (Electric Vehicle)\n6. **Tata Tigor EV** (Electric Vehicle)\n\n### Commercial Vehicles (Some of the popular ones):\n1. **Tata Ace**\n2. **Tata Prima**\n3. **Tata Ultra**\n4. **Tata Xenon**\n\nPlease note that the models listed above may include different variants with various features, trims, and specifications. For the most accurate and updated information, including new launches or discontinued models, you should check Tata Motors' official website or visit a Tata Motors dealership.",
